      Methods in com.polarion.alm.shared.api.model that return ModelObjectReference 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      ModelObjectReference ModelObjectReference.getCurrent()
      Returns the reference to current revision of the object, in other words reference without requested revision and actual revision.
      ModelObjectReference ModelObject.getReference() 
      ModelObjectReference ModelObject.getReferenceToCurrent()
      Returns reference without requested and actual revisions, so it is much faster than ModelObject.getReference(), because it does not have to read the actual revision.
      ModelObjectReference ModelObjectReference.getWithRevision(java.lang.String requestedRevision)
      Returns the reference to the same object, but with different requestedRevision(), the actualRevision() of the returned reference is null.
      Methods in com.polarion.alm.shared.api.model that return types with arguments of type ModelObjectReference 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
